Package: mixology
Title: Sentiment Analysis Lexicons and Tools for Covid-19 Crisis Communication
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Laurence", "Dierickx", email = "hello@ohmybox.info", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides two manually annotated sentiment lexicons developed for
    opinion mining of Twitter data during the Covid-19 crisis (December 2021,
    Western Europe): the Mixology Covid Lexicon (4,166 terms) and the Mixology
    Lexicon (16,528 terms, merged from six general-purpose dictionaries).
    Also includes a custom English stop words list (350 terms) and a negation
    markers list (22 terms). Provides helper functions for tokenisation,
    negation-aware sentiment scoring, and weighted sentiment analysis.
